00:03:19.389 --> 00:03:23.152
First I want to tell you what
goes wrong with Newtonian

00:03:23.152 --> 00:03:23.990
mechanics.
 

00:03:23.990 --> 00:03:26.674
After all, if everything is a
particle, what's the big deal,

00:03:26.674 --> 00:03:27.628
what's the problem?
 

00:03:27.628 --> 00:03:30.180
The double slit experiment is a
problem.

00:03:30.180 --> 00:03:33.593
That's what puts the nail on
the coffin for Newtonian

00:03:33.593 --> 00:03:36.680
physics, and here it is in the
basic version.

00:03:36.680 --> 00:03:38.710
You've got two slits.
 

00:03:38.710 --> 00:03:41.270
By the way, I'm going to call
the particle the electron.

00:03:41.270 --> 00:03:45.079
They're all doing the same
thing, so what applies to one,

00:03:45.079 --> 00:03:46.780
applies to all of them.
 

00:03:46.780 --> 00:03:50.491
There is a source,
like an electron gun,

00:03:50.491 --> 00:03:52.680
that emits electrons.
 

00:03:52.680 --> 00:03:57.555
In the old days,
televisions had the electron

00:03:57.555 --> 00:03:58.220
gun.
 

00:03:58.220 --> 00:04:01.269
And the gun emits the
electrons, they go and hit the

00:04:01.269 --> 00:04:04.917
screen, they make a little dot,
and then the dot moves around,

00:04:04.917 --> 00:04:07.008
