a definite momentum.

00:04:14.158 --> 00:04:16.613
That you can get by
accelerating the electrons over

00:04:16.613 --> 00:04:18.774
a definite potential,
and the gain of so many

00:04:18.774 --> 00:04:21.180
electron volts will turn into
kinetic energy.

00:04:21.180 --> 00:04:24.386
As for direction,
