00:04:24.386 --> 00:04:26.745
to the left,
in principle 1 mile,

00:04:26.745 --> 00:04:30.817
then the only way electrons are
going to go 1 mile and hit the

00:04:30.817 --> 00:04:34.488
screen is they're all basically
moving in the horizontal

00:04:34.488 --> 00:04:35.490
direction.
 

00:04:35.490 --> 00:04:41.329
Then you put a row of detectors
in the back, which will detect

00:04:41.329 --> 00:04:42.480
