00:04:52.586 --> 00:04:56.860
what do we really know when we
do the experiment?

00:04:56.860 --> 00:04:59.622
Once in a while this gun will
emit an electron,

00:04:59.622 --> 00:05:03.226
and we know it's emitted the
electron, because it will recoil

00:05:03.226 --> 00:05:05.389
one way, just like a gun,
rifle.

00:05:05.389 --> 00:05:06.399
It will recoil.
 

00:05:06.399 --> 00:05:09.769
That's when we know the
electron left.

00:05:09.769 --> 00:05:13.175
Then we don't know anything,
and suddenly,

00:05:13.175 --> 00:05:15.750
one of these guys says click.
 

00:05:15.750 --> 00:05:18.819
That means electron's arrived
here.

00:05:18.819 --> 00:05:21.250
This is what we really know.
 

00:05:21.250 --> 00:05:24.353
Everything else you say about
the electron is conjecture at

00:05:24.353 --> 00:05:25.050
this point.
 

00:05:25.050 --> 00:05:27.410
You know it was here,
you know it was there.

00:05:27.410 --> 00:05:31.620
The question is,
what was it doing in between?

00:05:31.620 --> 00:05:34.291
Now if you say,
"Look, things cannot go

00:05:34.291 --> 00:05:37.336
from here to there,
except by following some path,

00:05:37.336 --> 00:05:39.759
I don't know what path it
is."

00:05:39.759 --> 00:05:41.209
Maybe if it's an ordinary
particle,

00:05:41.209 --> 00:05:43.514
like a Newtonian particle,
it will take some straight

00:05:43.514 --> 00:05:45.028
line,
hit that slit,

00:05:45.028 --> 00:05:48.420
or go through that slit and
arrive here.

00:05:48.420 --> 00:05:52.177
So you might say,
"I don't know the

00:05:52.177 --> 00:05:56.608
trajectory, but it's got to be
some trajectory,

00:05:56.608 --> 00:06:01.040
maybe like that,
or maybe like that."

00:06:01.040 --> 00:06:06.615
So the electron takes some path
and you can label the path as

00:06:06.615 --> 00:06:10.519
either through slit 1 or through
slit 2.

00:06:10.519 --> 00:06:13.740
Okay, now here is the problem.
 

00:06:13.740 --> 00:06:17.000
Suppose I do the experiment
with slit 2 blocked,

00:06:17.000 --> 00:06:19.199
so you cannot even get through
this one,

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:22.850
and I sit at a certain location
for a certain amount of time,

00:06:22.850 --> 00:06:25.759
maybe 1 hour and I see how many
electrons come,

00:06:25.759 --> 00:06:31.040
