00:10:42.570 --> 00:10:45.416
That means nobody comes here,
a lot of them come here,

00:10:45.416 --> 00:10:47.940
no one comes here,
a few come here and so on.

00:10:47.940 --> 00:10:48.850
That's what you find.
 

